        Approve product designs before production.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc">
        Trust over 6 years experience of professional 3D and product design. All while offering a fresh take on product design and design in general.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="cover">
        <img
                  src="/works/website-mock-ups.webp"
                  class="w-full rounded duration-200 hover:shadow-sm"
                />
      </Fragment>
    </SlotHero>

          <SectionHeadImg>
            <Fragment slot="smltitle">
              Digital and Print Graphic Design
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="title">
              Complete brand design packages for all platforms and mediums.
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="desc">
              Looking for top-notch Gold Coast graphic designer to boost your brands prescence? With over six years of experience in optimizing conversion rates for Wordpress stores and funnels, we're your go-to experts for creating stunning and user-friendly e-commerce websites. Our primary focus is on UX design, ensuring that your customers have a seamless and enjoyable shopping experience from start to finish.
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="cover">
              <img
                        src="/works/br-mac-render-med.webp"
                        class="w-full rounded duration-200 hover:shadow-sm"
                      />
            </Fragment>
          </SectionHeadImg>

          <SectionHeadSecImg>
            <Fragment slot="smltitle">
              Improving conversion rate through design
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="title">
              An expert in improving funnel conversion rate.
            </Fragment>
